    "intro": {
      "headline": "Love is a long position.",
      "year": "2022",
      "role": "Senior Copywriter",
      "body": [
        "Crypto brands don't do Valentine's Day. That was exactly the point.",
        "We leaned into the language of trading to talk about love — because for our audience, the two aren't as different as you'd think."
